{"id":1667753,"retrievedAt":"2026-04-11T11:51:11.523Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":99,"name":"Documentary"}],"homepage":"https://kinoteka.mk/filmovi/in-continuo/","id":1667753,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["MK"],"original_language":"la","original_title":"In Continuo","overview":"This film was made in 1998 and was dedicated to the 50th anniversary of the Exodus of the children from the Aegean part of Macedonia during the Greek Civil War. Using historical facts, archival material and actual film footage, the film tells the story of the genocide of the Macedonian people in this part of Macedonia. In the spring of 1948, over 28.000 Macedonian children left Greece and sought refuge across the border into the Vardar part of Macedonia and eventually into other countries such as Poland, Romania, Hungary and Czechoslovakia. The archival footage depicts the children leaving as well as showing film taken in both world wars.","popularity":0.0143,"poster_path":null,"production_companies":[{"id":28208,"logo_path":null,"name":"Vardar Film","origin_country":"MK"}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"MK","name":"Macedonia"}],"release_date":"1998-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":109,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"Macedonian","iso_639_1":"mk","name":""}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"In Continuo","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":6132707,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Simon Beličanec","original_name":"Simon Beličanec","popularity":0,"profile_path":null,"cast_id":8,"character":"Narrator (voice)","credit_id":"69d9345cc31e2c4d1937215e","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":6132711,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Liljana Krsteva","original_name":"Liljana Krsteva","popularity":0,"profile_path":null,"cast_id":9,"character":"Narrator (voice)","credit_id":"69d934880c681f559e7097fb","